{"tid":1552031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港國旗】 不可抽氣扇，不可龍獅章","createTime":"2019-09-08T09:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T15:19:48.000Z","uid":299171,"like":43,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"c29c8f47e1a001eb9b35b756b4e85e9357deabe1","tid":1552031,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bBoLgv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bBoLgv.png&h=17cc5194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不可抽氣扇原因</span></strong><br />\n1. 洋紫荊係雜交得來嘅花，雜種<br />\n2. 洋紫荊不可繁衍，絕後<br />\n3. 抽氣扇花瓣非向外，寓意自封大門，轉極停留原點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUJqYCj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUJqYCj.png&h=e582441e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不可龍獅章原因</strong></span><br />\n1. 小獅子（英軍）從龍（中國）手上拎走龍珠（香港）俾大獅子（英國），咁係直接承認香港屬於中國，萬萬不可。<br />\n2. 英國奶緊共，仲黐埋去？"},{"pid":"5fc64243f72cdd2b21c5c9d79868a561768acf8c","tid":1552031,"uid":182933,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:20:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"baffe764ad549de07caf102ef9e82877e6ab5dba","tid":1552031,"uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:21:33.000Z","msg":"pepe the frog"},{"pid":"f82378ebd968f4cb35fe0f0dd87ed29ec8e1bcdc","tid":1552031,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:22:16.000Z","msg":"三色旗最好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5e7bf23552b373f92e188ecb0f1e9fc8d28a9e","tid":1552031,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:22:38.000Z","msg":"黑底<br />\n黃色獅子山係中間<br />\n點睇"},{"pid":"8395bb56756ef9bf88ff89e36227db6b4d412da4","tid":1552031,"uid":17510,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"c29c8f47e1a001eb9b35b756b4e85e9357deabe1","tid":1552031,"uid"