9e2f2c6aa100d1a9ce719e375352","tid":1552031,"uid":265439,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6JobhqB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6JobhqB.png&h=e0cbce4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自由<br />\n革命(黃傘)<br />\n人民(抗爭者)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:49:53.000Z","msg":"同你差唔多<br />\n但我既係黃黑藍"},{"pid":"d4c9508ab86e865551d9137d11a5877da8ba8997","tid":1552031,"uid":126283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"嘗試鳩譯一下黃黑藍旗：<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者形態：<br />\n黃：黃傘（民主）<br />\n黑：黑衣（自由）<br />\n藍：流水形式既運動（團結）<br />\n<br />\n呢三個元素我覺得可以做埋香港既格言<br />\n<br />\n歷史演譯：<br />\n想用色調表達香港既由來<br />\n黃：大清國黃龍旗既底色<br />\n黑：黑屬水，而香港作為轉口港，靠貿易、航海發展，呢兩個行業都係同水有關<br />\n藍：英國米字旗既海軍藍<br />\n<br />\n意即香港從清國割讓予英國管治，受東西文化影響下逢勃發展"},{"pid":"4a02f69e063836bdb025c2ae1ecceb73a9df58ef","tid":1552031,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:42:54.000Z","msg":"脫支再諗未遲"},{"pid":"70c689740c31dd858d9951bb6e8cb7ae562f7c55","tid":1552031,"uid":20518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"adb90164f577955177008e5cc47036c265ad8078","tid":1552031,"uid":212182,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSPxNaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSPxNaa.jpg&h=882b0b3c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jRo29oB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjRo29oB.jpg&h=34c640e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:46:39.000Z","msg":"真心我覺得呢個係幾有意思<br />\n<br />\n不過可能有d人覺得太花"},{"pid":"e7f7f171cc30afa31ac37a463ba81a0917620296","tid":1552031,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:50:41.000Z","msg":"象徵意義<br />\n<br />\n每種顏色有其象徵意義<br />\n<br />\n黃：光明、希望<br />\n黑：力量<br />\n藍：智慧