香港屬於中國，萬萬不可。<br />\n2. 英國奶緊共，仲黐埋去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:52:35.000Z","msg":"黑旗 我中意黑旗多D"},{"pid":"8ad27c763ab64f8fc3bd27d1323f8662f1a21e93","tid":1552031,"uid":309049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"adb90164f577955177008e5cc47036c265ad8078","tid":1552031,"uid":212182,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSPxNaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSPxNaa.jpg&h=882b0b3c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jRo29oB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjRo29oB.jpg&h=34c640e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:53:21.000Z","msg":"呢個其實幾ok"},{"pid":"c57281b60d686e9ae2430210308aadd735213e7e","tid":1552031,"uid":222451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:55:27.000Z","msg":"龍獅章中間改做phoenix得唔得<br />\n係東西文明(龍, 獅)中孕育而生, 再浴火重生成為別於東西兩方既新星"},{"pid":"2e308f93ce422903166fab980c725c815f837327","tid":1552031,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"仆街原來支區旗都係要做九我地"},{"pid":"75cf54d113a19fac0d20ff89d13c052633a3b34a","tid":1552031,"uid":50719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SzmPPPp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzmPPPp.png&h=5ab7ae4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f25f5323df7642c805bd6dea2c6b8b752b053cd4","tid":1552031,"uid":183856,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a2sWuPK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa2sWuPK.png&h=4a40c04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n代表住香港歷史嘅國旗"},{"pid":"3b634bb4967dfdc3116b3aff548984a1651f2b26","tid":1552031,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e308f93ce422903166fab980c