Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zng76Jt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZng76Jt.png&h=72da44ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"負皮，不過欣賞你唧創意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c4021d4afafb71a8e6d6d1556d99312c773c89","tid":1552031,"uid":265192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8ad27c763ab64f8fc3bd27d1323f8662f1a21e93","tid":1552031,"uid":309049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"adb90164f577955177008e5cc47036c265ad8078","tid":1552031,"uid":212182,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSPxNaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSPxNaa.jpg&h=882b0b3c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jRo29oB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjRo29oB.jpg&h=34c640e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:53:21.000Z","msg":"呢個其實幾ok"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:15:32.000Z","msg":"百家布 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b6a520cfe58398f7cbda0a2e24c90ee94172ef","tid":1552031,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c5ed411442132b5ab69fa194d91e990a21f087d","tid":1552031,"uid":235152,"like":6,"dislike":25,"score":-19,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/flags/109.jpg?v=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fflags%2F109.jpg%3Fv%3D1&h=372e409a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國旗用色以英國旗為基調配以暖黃突出國徽 紀念香港以英國文化之形響下成為集東西文化於一身之國度 國徽概念以洋紫荆之形浴火重生，以大鵬金翅鳥之形相重現 象徵香港歷中共浩刼而後自強獨立成國，必然有更美好前景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/flags/110.jpg?v=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fflags%2F110.jpg%3Fv%3D1&h=7711a38e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獅子山旗&mdash; 國旗由藍、白兩個平行相等的長方形及具象化的獅子山組成。正中的獅子象徵香港人不屈不撓的精神，中間的星代表港人獨立的意志和決心。藍色代表民主，自由；白色代表和平，公正。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/flags/94.jpg?v=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fflags%2F94.jpg%3Fv%3D1&h=f927caf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n木棉有英雄樹之稱，象徵香港雄視亞東；其花落不散，喻各地國民皆心繫母國；十八花蕊象徵十八區國民子嗣繁衍。金黃雲雷紋拱衛木棉，香港建國順天應人，承繼華夏。普魯士藍底色，象徵海洋，呼應英治。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:18:17.000Z","msg":"中間好靚，不過好中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n似魯魯修"},{"pid":"3f14241ffdec20dcbedc9592cd45194ad13ea621","tid":1552031,"uid":265192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4uDuPVP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4uDuPVP.png&h=6ce887b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7182d300d1858c3effd90c0063e5b6dc231dfaff","tid":1552031,"uid":118520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c29c8f47e1a001eb9b35b756b4e85e9357deabe1","tid":1552031,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bBoLgv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bBoLgv.png&h=17cc5194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不可抽氣扇原因</span></strong><br />\n1. 洋紫荊係雜交得來嘅花，雜種<br />\n2. 洋紫荊不可繁衍，絕後<br />\n3. 抽氣扇花瓣非向外，寓意自封大門，轉極停留原點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUJqYCj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUJqYCj.png&h=e582441e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不可龍獅章原因</strong></span><br />\n1. 小獅子（英軍）從龍（中國）手上拎走龍珠（香港）俾大獅子（英國），咁係直接承認香港屬於中國，萬萬不可。<br />\n2. 英國奶緊共，仲黐埋去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:21:11.000Z","msg":"但97淪陷前都用緊龍獅喎"},{"pid":"47be1b515219770b62bd7452ee911e09305ecbad