0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oEpBvdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoEpBvdt.jpg&h=57f93678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攞返之前熱狗搞嘅國旗設計比賽， 唔好睇佢嗰支旗好似mono擦膠咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 其實佢呢個格局令我諗返起德意志帝國嘅格局<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3ZU1kQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3ZU1kQ.png&h=7e7dc755&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81761934ce4da6fd4f4a2ae9f54fca3b3e9f11b4","tid":1552031,"uid":290468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c5ed411442132b5ab69fa194d91e990a21f087d","tid":1552031,"uid":235152,"like":6,"dislike":25,"score":-19,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/flags/109.jpg?v=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fflags%2F109.jpg%3Fv%3D1&h=372e409a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國旗用色以英國旗為基調配以暖黃突出國徽 紀念香港以英國文化之形響下成為集東西文化於一身之國度 國徽概念以洋紫荆之形浴火重生，以大鵬金翅鳥之形相重現 象徵香港歷中共浩刼而後自強獨立成國，必然有更美好前景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/flags/110.jpg?v=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fflags%2F110.jpg%3Fv%3D1&h=7711a38e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獅子山旗&mdash; 國旗由藍、白兩個平行相等的長方形及具象化的獅子山組成。正中的獅子象徵香港人不屈不撓的精神，中間的星代表港人獨立的意志和決心。藍色代表民主，自由；白色代表和平，公正。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/flags/94.jpg?v=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fflags%2F94.jpg%3Fv%3D1&h=f927caf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n木棉有英雄樹之稱，象徵香港雄視亞東；其花落不散，喻各地國民皆心繫母國；十八花蕊象徵十八區國民子嗣繁衍。金黃雲雷紋拱衛木棉，香港建國順天應人，承繼華夏。普魯士藍底色，象徵海洋，呼應英治。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:17:41.000Z","msg":"2號旗幾靚，不過太強未來感，似高達入面會出現既某組織旗多過現實世界會出現既國旗"},{"pid":"c81f34abae299ff4e1a60be4202ffe5145f931cd","tid":1552031,"uid":290468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f14241ffdec20dcb